            <span id="MainContent_DataListTypes_LabelType_3"><h2 class="title"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Apprentice [<a href="TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Apprentice" style="font-color: white">Link</a>]</h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy9nvh?Pathfinder-Player-Companion-Divine-Anthology" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Divine Anthology pg. 9</i></a><br />During your studies of <i>The Majestic Book of the Prime Ascended</i>, you learned some minor magical tricks. Select a single 0-level spell from the sorcerer/ wizard spell list. You can cast this spell 1 time per day as a spell-like ability. <br /><br /></span>
